rating_comment: Our experience was truly delightful. Accompanied by my family, we found immense satisfaction with the accommodation. The host, remained readily available whenever assistance was required. Good location. Had an excellent stay within budget. Overall great experience. Recommended.

Really great location for travellers from NJP bus stand, good place to spend time while waiting for your bus.
Stay was clean and spacious, and comfortable.

I like the hospitality of north east part of India and it begined at this stay. Digvijay is amazing host, always available for all the queries , nice peaceful stay. Spacious property. Served nice home cooked meal.
I would love to stay here again
